dialogue.name: Yeah, baby! All eyes on me, and don't you dare look away, else you get burned! Wooo!
Hell yeah, this fire keeps burning, baby!
If you liked that, you haven't seen nothing yet! I can go even crazier!
Maybe all the yelling is starting to throw out my voice... Nah! Let's go much louder next time!
Urghh... I can feel the burnout kicking in. This suuuuuucks.
